    • busiestDivisionTab

      public void busiestDivisionTab(javafx.event.Event event)
      This method calculates the busiest division based on number of appointments it has, by iterating through all first level divisions and counting the number of appointments each one has. It then displays the data in the busiestDivisionTable and adjusts the busiestDivisionLabel
      Parameters:
      event - When the busiestDivision tab is selected
